                                <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">SHANKARACHARYA</a></h3>
                                <p>It is located on the top of Zabarwan Hill at a height of 1,000 feet above the valley floor.</p>
                                <div class="blog-author">
                                    
                                </div>
                            </div>
