                                <div class="blog-date"><p><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>Srinagar</p></div>
                                <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">HAZRATBAL SHRINE</a></h3>
                                <p>Dargah hazratbal shrine is located near the Famous Dal lake. It takes around 11 years to complete its famous mosque.</p>
