                        <div class="blog-post-detail">
                            <div class="blog-content blog-content-1">
                                <div class="blog-date"><p><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>Srinagar</p></div>
                                <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">MANASBAL</a></h3>
                                <p>The lake is a good place for birdwatching as it is one of the largest natural stamping grounds of Aquatic birds in Kashmir and has the sobriquet of "supreme gem of all Kashmir Lakes".</p>
                                <div class="blog-author">
                                </div>
                            </div>
